{"type":"message","id":"368ff434","parentId":"b2def6b7","timestamp":"2026-02-17T19:34:48.956Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Refining Execution Protocols**\n\nI've identified a critical flaw in the Windows environment: the absence of `grep`. This caused the script to fail. The directory existence error isn't critical, but it contributed to the cascading failure. Moving forward, I am focusing on using alternative methods for searching, such as PowerShell, and refining the error handling in the `broadcast_log.py` script. The \"message\" tool's failure is also being addressed.\n\n\n**Adjusting Extraction Strategy**\n\nThe PowerShell equivalent of `grep` is in place, specifically using `Select-String` to mimic the pattern matching. I've accounted for the output format differences, aiming to align with the original `grep` behavior by including the filename in the output. I'm now proceeding to execute the modified extraction script and re-run the broadcast.\n\n\n**Revising Log Filtering**\n\nI've tested the PowerShell equivalent of the `grep` command, using `Select-String`, and will now execute it. I'm accounting for differences in output formatting, particularly the inclusion of filenames, to ensure the extracted data remains consistent with the original design. I will report the final message using environment variables or fallback output.\n\n\n**Finalizing Execution and Reporting**\n\nI've revised the PowerShell command for log extraction using `Select-String`, directly targeting the log files. It also seems I'm okay with `Select-String`'s default output format. Now the script will run, and the broadcast will be re-attempted. I will report back the \"Broadcaster Active. Stand by.\" message, using either the environment's `chat_id` or directly outputting the text.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1771356888944_136","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Select-String -Pattern 'ERROR|WARN|TIMEOUT|CRITICAL|Traceback' -Path 'logs/performance_audit.log', 'logs/bot_*.log' | Out-File -Encoding UTF8 reports/ALL_ISSUES_RAW.md\""},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":6266,"output":876,"cacheRead":4981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":7142,"cost":{"input":0.012532,"output":0.010512,"cacheRead":0.0009962,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0240402}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771356874648}}
